idth>105</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>2925</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>OtherPhotos</PhotoType></Photo><Photo><Url>/RXLImages/1014/JAC36043_12.JPG</Url><Width>400</Width><Height>267</Height><Bytes>27456</Bytes><Caption /><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/1014/JAC36043Thumb_12.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>105</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>2737</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>OtherPhotos</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>Rose in Vale is a Grade II Listed country house hotel offering a peaceful and luxurious place to stay on the North Cornish coast in the village of Mithian, just 2 miles from St Agnes. The hotel has real fires, a drawing room and library for guests to relax in. The Valley Restaurant has been awarded an AA Rosette and has a fine dining menu of fresh, local produce and serves a fabulous English breakfast in the morning! The elegant bedrooms are fitted with individually controlled central heating, a TV and radio as well as tea and coffee-making facilities. There is a seasonal outdoor swimming pool, free Wi-Fi and plenty of parking for guests. Friendly staff are knowledgeable about the area and can provide sightseeing information. There are many fantastic walking routes surrounding the hotel and fishing, water sports and horse riding are nearby. The hotel is exclusive for adults with no children under years of age 12 accepted.</Text></Description><Rating><System>Stars</System><Score>40</Score><Description>Four star</Description></Rating><Rank>1</Rank></HotelElement>